Agent: Oh haan, bilkul! Aapne Trimfinity 3 in 1 face trimmer apne cart mein add kiya tha. Yeh ek advanced trimmer hai jo face ke saath body ke liye bhi perfect hai. Price ₹1899 hai, lekin agar aap interested hain, toh main aapke liye ek special 5% discount ka offer kar sakta hoon. Aapko koi aur detail chahiye iske baare mein?
User: Coupon भेज दीजिए.
Agent: Bilkul Ankit ji! Aapke liye ek exclusive coupon code hai: O-F-F-5. Isse aapko 5% ka discount milega. Main abhi aapko WhatsApp pe ek checkout link bhej deta hoon, jisme yeh coupon already apply hoga. Aap bas uspe click karke payment complete kar sakte hain. Theek hai?
